arts.ttl: Frank can solve specific "problem" with Copenhagen win, ex-Spurs midfielder claims
arts.sum: Tottenham Hotspur can solve a major Thomas Frank "problem" with victory over Copenhagen in Tuesday's Champions League clash in North London, a former Spurs midfielder tells Sports Mole.

arts.ttl: Tottenham vs FC Copenhagen predictions: Spurs ready to win a thriller
arts.sum: Tottenham take on Denmark's FC Copenhagen in the Champions League on Tuesday and Gareth Freeman expects Spurs to prevail in an entertaining clash.
